trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Dá suporte de tempo de design em um designer visual para o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Generates the HTML markup that is used to render the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" /> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Gera a marcação HTML usada para renderizar o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" /> associado em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The HTML markup that is used to render the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" /> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: A marcação HTML usada para renderizar o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager" /> associado em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to generate a simple rectangular placeholder representation that displays the type and ID of the control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.Design.DynamicDataManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> chamadas de método de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A> método para gerar uma representação de espaço reservado de retangular simples que exibe o tipo e a identificação do controle.
